Squid Farm Privacy Policy

This is a demo application for educational purposes.

Data Collection:
- We collect minimal data for game functionality
- Telegram user ID is stored locally
- No personal information is shared with third parties

Data Usage:
- User data is used only for game mechanics
- Production statistics are calculated locally
- No tracking or analytics

Data Storage:
- Data is stored locally in your browser
- Backend stores only game progress
- No sensitive information is collected

Contact: For questions about privacy, contact the development team.
